trans-unit.source: Provides specific XAML writer settings for <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gir spesifikke XAML writer-innstillinger for <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter> can function within specified XamlObjectWriterSettings.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>kan funksjonen i angitte XamlObjectWriterSettings.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>

trans-unit.source: Where settings are not specified, an instance of XamlObjectWriterSettings exists that has default values for a constructed <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>, and this instance can be used in merges of settings for a derived class.
trans-unit.target: Der innstillinger ikke er angitt, en forekomst av XamlObjectWriterSettings finnes som har standardverdier for en konstruert <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>, og denne forekomsten kan brukes i flettinger innstillingene for en avledet klasse.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>

trans-unit.source: This property indicates the expected access level for non-public members, which are accessed in partial trust through a partial-trust tolerant runtime.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the XAML namescope to use for registering names from the XAML writer if <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriterSettings.RegisterNamesOnExternalNamescope*> is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir XAML namescope skal brukes for å registrere navn fra XAML skriveren hvis <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriterSettings.RegisterNamesOnExternalNamescope*>er <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriterSettings.RegisterNamesOnExternalNamescope*>

trans-unit.source: Specific contexts for a <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter> might use an external XAML namescope.
trans-unit.target: Bestemte kontekster for en <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>kan bruke en ekstern XAML namescope.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>

trans-unit.source: WPF Usage Notes In the WPF XAML implementation, XAML writer operations that are initiated by <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkTemplate> specify a separate XAML namescope.
trans-unit.target: WPF Bruk merknader i det WPF XAML implementering, XAML writer operasjoner som er startet av <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkTemplate>Angi en egen XAML namescope.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkTemplate>

trans-unit.source: In this WPF scenario, templates should not share a XAML namescope with the root of the XAML page that defines them.
trans-unit.target: I dette WPF scenariet bør maler ikke dele en XAML namescope med roten av siden XAML som definerer dem.

trans-unit.source: Instead, they should process into a separate, designated XAML namescope.
trans-unit.target: De må i stedet behandle i en separat, angitt XAML namescope.

trans-unit.source: The XAML namescope to use for registering names.
trans-unit.target: XAML-namescope skal brukes for å registrere navn.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the XAML writer should ignore (not call) <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom*> implementations on a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter"></xref> in type-converter situations.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om XAML skriveren skal ignorere (ikke kall) <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom*>implementeringer på en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter"> </xref> i typekonvertering situasjoner.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom*>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter> class and its <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom%2A> method are part of an overall design for type conversion in the CLR.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>klassen og <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom%2A>metoden er en del av en generelle utformingen for typekonvertering i CLR.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>

trans-unit.source: In XAML systems, you can typically assume that type-converter input is identifiable by the XAML reader, and for purposes of input, is always a string.
trans-unit.target: I XAML systemer, kan du vanligvis anta at typekonvertering inndataene identifiserbar av XAML leseren og for å inndataene, er alltid en streng.

trans-unit.source: If you set this property to `true`, you enable a mode where this assumption is codified in the XAML object writer behavior.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du setter denne egenskapen til `true`, en modus der denne forutsetningen codified i XAML objektet writer virkemåte aktiveres.

trans-unit.source: This mode supports a compatibility requirement for previous versions of WPF XAML.
trans-unit.target: Denne modusen støtter et krav for kompatibilitet for tidligere versjoner av WPF XAML.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the XAML writer ignores <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom*> implementations; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis XAML skriveren ignorerer <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom*>implementeringer; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.CanConvertFrom*>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines whether to disable a default feature that runs type conversion on the K component of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> before writing the object graph representation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som bestemmer om å deaktivere standard funksjon som kjører skriver konvertering i den K sekundkomponenten for en <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> før sideinnholdet objektet diagrammet representasjonen.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the `K` type conversion feature, see Remarks in <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om den `K` type konverteringsfunksjonen, må du se kommentarer i <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>

trans-unit.source: if K type conversion for a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> object should be disabled.
trans-unit.target: Hvis K typen konverteringen for en <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> objektet skal deaktiveres.

trans-unit.source: if performing K type conversion for a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> object applies.
trans-unit.target: Hvis utfører K typen konverteringen for en <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602> objektet gjelder.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if name registration should occur against the <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriterSettings.ExternalNameScope*>; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if name registration should occur into the parent XAML namescope.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a preexisting root object for <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter"></xref> operations.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en eksisterende rotobjekt for <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter"> </xref> operasjoner.

trans-unit.source: If you set this value, the root object instance is used as an implicit <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter.WriteStartObject%2A> call (with object input that is direct instead of coming from the reader) that precedes the first explicit node-write call by the <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du setter denne verdien, roten objektforekomsten brukes som en implisitt <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter.WriteStartObject%2A>kall (med objektet inndata som er direkte i stedet for kommer fra leseren) som kommer før det første kallet eksplisitt node-og skrivetilgang av <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter>.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter> </xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter.WriteStartObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: Any error checking, such as verifying the XAML type of the provided root object, is deferred until that implicit <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter.WriteStartObject%2A> call, instead of being checked when you set this settings property.
trans-unit.target: Alle feilkontroll, for eksempel kontrollerer XAML-typen for det angitte rotobjektet er utsatt før som implisitt <xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter.WriteStartObject%2A>kall, i stedet for sjekkes når du angir denne egenskapen i innstillingene.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter.WriteStartObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: A preexisting root object for <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter"></xref> operations.
trans-unit.target: En tidligere rotobjekt for <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlObjectWriter"> </xref> operasjoner.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines whether the XAML writer omits to check for the code path that checks for duplicate properties.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som bestemmer om XAML skriveren utelater å se etter kodebane søker etter dupliserte egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: The specified code path checks the currently assigned properties and throws an exception if a duplicate property set of the named ambient property is attempted.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte kodebanen kontrollerer gjeldende tilordnede egenskaper og oppstår det et unntak hvis dupliserte settet med navngitte omkringliggende egenskapen forsøkes.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Xaml.IAmbientProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Xaml.IAmbientProvider>.</xref:System.Xaml.IAmbientProvider>

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis dupliserte kontroller må utelates; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen gjelder for malen og utsette load scenarier.
